  "text": "Lenovo IdeaPad Duet 5 $299 $499 Save $200 A solid Chromebook that can transform into a tablet or laptop thanks to its removable keyboard. Plus, you get a beautiful OLED screen, along with plenty of power under the hood. Get it now for just $299 thanks to this discount from Best Buy. If you're looking for a device that can pull double duty as a laptop and tablet, this Lenovo Chromebook is going to be just the thing. The IdeaPad Duet 5 not only features a versatile design, but you also get a beautiful OLED screen and excellent power under the hood. Furthermore, it's not all that expensive right now thanks to a steep discount from Best Buy that drops the price by $200. Act fast and you can grab this excellent Chromebook for just $299. Related Best 2-in-1 Chromebooks in 2025 Enjoy Chrome OS the way you want to What's great about the IdeaPad Duet 5? This is one of those devices that really flies under the radar, but delivers an experience that's worth every penny at $299. It's powered by a Qualcomm Snapdragon 7c Gen 2 chip that's paired with 8GB of RAM and 128GB of internal storage. You also get a vibrant 13.3-inch OLED screen that great for games, movies, and browsing the web. Of course, the real highlight here is the versatile design that allows it to transform into a tablet or laptop. And with ChromeOS, you get tons of power at your fingertips, allowing you to access tools from the cloud and also download apps to your device as needed. When it comes to battery life, things are quite good, with up to ten hours of use on a single charge. For the most part, this is going to be a great device to carry around, offering a great mix of portability and power. It can be your main entertainment device, or get you through some work while you're on the go. At its newly discounted price of $299, it becomes a no-brainer if you're looking for a 2-in-1 laptop. Just be sure to grab it while it's still on sale.",
